{
    "name": "Tarn Linnorm",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Although legends speak of even more powerful linnorms, it\u2019s hard to believe after witnessing the devastation a two-headed tarn linnorm can wreak. Content to slumber away the centuries at the bottom of dark mountain lakes, the tarn linnorms are true horrors that even the mightiest of heroes fear.<br/><br/>A tarn linnorm is 120 feet long and weighs 24,000 pounds."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>This nightmarishly huge, snake-like dragon possesses two equally fearsome heads. Its twin jaws seethe with acid and poison.</i>",
